value.0: These are definitely the droids you are looking for.
Use this on a resource to harvest it.

Use this on a resource to identify its contents. Use it on a location to identify where the nearest resource is.

Scanners grant XP when used for the first time on resources. They also increase the XP gained for each subsequent harvesting attempt performed by the player who scanned it. Finally, they improve the chance to receive a bonus item property on harvested resources.
This can be placed inside refineries to power them for a short time.
Removes the effect of "Bleed" from your target. Also recovers a small amount of HP. Use speed is increased based on your First Aid rank.
Heals a target for 2 HP every 6 seconds for a duration of 30 seconds. Length of time is increased with higher skill ranks in Medicine
Removes poison and disease from your target. Use speed is increased based on your Medicine rank.
